All the profits went to the trading company, and the farmers

00:06:56.735 --> 00:07:01.978
were in effective slavery to their so-called trading partners.

00:07:03.308 --> 00:07:09.678
So the first ethical Fairtrade coffee was named after this book, Max Havelaar.

00:07:10.628 --> 00:07:12.788
And it was a huge success, the coffee.

00:07:13.845 --> 00:07:20.265
Max Havelaar coffee paid its farmers more than the market price, more than

00:07:20.265 --> 00:07:25.935
the standard price they would get in the market, and importantly, it guaranteed the price.

00:07:27.165 --> 00:07:32.055
This was shown to be very important because the year after

00:07:32.085 --> 00:07:37.575
Max Havelaar launched coffee prices around the world crashed.

